{"id":"apgar_score","version":"0.0.1","templates":[{"id":"apgar_score","version":"0.1.0"}],"language":"en","updated":"2021-08-17T15:17:28+02:00","authors":[{"name":"Maryam Razavi","email":"maryam.razavi@cambio.se"}],"format":"CambioForm.v1","name":"apgar_score","guidelines":[{"condition":"respiratory_effort && heart_rate && muscle_tone && reflex_irritability && skin_colour","execution":[{"id":"Apgar","version":"1"}]}],"elements":[{"type":"form","children":[{"type":"container","hidden":false,"readonly":false,"children":[{"type":"row","spanlarge":12,"spanmedium":8,"spansmall":4,"children":[{"type":"column","spanlarge":12,"spanmedium":8,"spansmall":4,"hidden":false,"readonly":false,"children":[{"text":"**APGAR Score**\n\nPerform on every live newborn, regardless of GA, at 1 and 5 minutes of life.\n\n\n\n- 60 seconds after complete delivery of the newborn was deemed the point of most marked depression.\n- Per Neonatal Resuscitation Program (NRP), scoring continues at 5 minute intervals until reaching a score of 7 or until 20 minutes of life is encountered.\n- Scored by any provider with direct patient contact at the specified time.\n\n\n\n**Formula**\n\nAddition of assigned points.\n\n- 5 independent items, each scored 0 (Absent), 1 (Intermediate), or 2 (Present)\n- Minimum score = 0; maximum = 10\n- Initial testing for “Reflex Irritability” was nasal and oropharyngeal suctioning with rubber catheter meant to elicit grimace, sneeze, or cough.\n- Later, a rapid, tangential slap of the sole of the foot was found to be an easier and more effective stimulus.\n\n\n\n## \n\n\n\n**Score interpretation:**\n\n\n\n- Scores ≥7; generally normal\n- Score of 4 to 6; fairly low\n- Scores ≤3; critically low, needs intervention","type":"text","size":"m","position":"left"}]}]},{"type":"row","spanlarge":12,"spanmedium":8,"spansmall":4,"hidden":false,"readonly":false,"children":[{"type":"column","spanlarge":6,"spanmedium":4,"spansmall":4,"hidden":false,"readonly":false,"children":[{"text":"Diagnosis Review","type":"label","size":"l","hidden":false,"position":"left","readonly":false},{"type":"input-select","label":"Respiratory effort","name":"respiratory_effort_5","options":[{"text":"Absent","value":"at0010","magnitude":0},{"text":"Weak or irregular","value":"at0011","magnitude":1},{"text":"Normal","value":"at0012","magnitude":2}],"clearable":true,"display":"buttons","hidden":false,"readonly":false,"required":true,"id":"respiratory_effort"},{"type":"input-select","label":"Heart rate","name":"heart_rate_5","options":[{"text":"Absent","value":"at0006","magnitude":0},{"text":"<100 beats per minute","value":"at0007","magnitude":1},{"text":"≥100 beats per minute","value":"at0008","magnitude":2}],"clearable":true,"display":"buttons","hidden":false,"readonly":false,"required":true,"id":"heart_rate"},{"type":"input-select","label":"Muscle tone","name":"muscle_tone_5","options":[{"text":"Limp or flaccid","value":"at0014","magnitude":0},{"text":"Reduced tone","value":"at0015","magnitude":1},{"text":"Normal tone","value":"at0016","magnitude":2}],"clearable":true,"display":"buttons","hidden":false,"readonly":false,"required":true,"id":"muscle_tone"},{"type":"input-select","label":"Reflex irritability","name":"reflex_irritability_5","options":[{"text":"No response","value":"at0018","magnitude":0},{"text":"Reduced response","value":"at0019","magnitude":1},{"text":"Normal response","value":"at0020","magnitude":2}],"clearable":true,"display":"buttons","hidden":false,"readonly":false,"required":true,"id":"reflex_irritability"},{"type":"input-select","label":"Skin colour","name":"skin_colour_5","options":[{"text":"Completely blue","value":"at0022","magnitude":0},{"text":"Body pink; extremities blue","value":"at0023","magnitude":1},{"text":"Completely pink","value":"at0024","magnitude":2}],"clearable":true,"display":"buttons","hidden":false,"readonly":false,"required":true,"id":"skin_colour"}]},{"type":"column","spanlarge":6,"spanmedium":4,"spansmall":4,"hidden":false,"readonly":false,"children":[{"text":"Apgar score & assessment","type":"label","size":"l","hidden":false,"position":"left","readonly":false},{"type":"input-count","label":"Total score","name":"total_score_5","min":0,"max":10,"readonly":true,"id":"total_score"},{"text":"Divider","type":"divider","size":"s"},{"type":"input-text","label":"Apgar assessment","name":"apgar_assessment","multiline":false,"readonly":true},{"text":"Spacer","type":"spacer","size":"m"}]}]},{"type":"reset-button","label":"Reset","display":"normal","hidden":false,"justify":"end","readonly":false},{"type":"submit-button","label":"Submit","justify":"end"}]}]}]}